BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Atlanta Experimental Fest
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260710T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260711T010000
DTSTAMP:20260710T203459Z
UID:occ-1706@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Film Screening
DESCRIPTION:A festival showcase of experimental film: abstract animation\,
  personal documentaries\, surreal narratives\, and handmade cinema.\n\nA f
 estival screening devoted to independent filmmakers working outside conven
 tional storytelling. The lineup ranges across abstract animation\, persona
 l documentaries\, surreal narratives\, handmade cinema\, and work that res
 ists genre labels altogether. Presented by 7 Stages\, the Little Five Poin
 ts company with a long history of experimental programming.
GEO:33.7639125;-84.3509364
LAST-MODIFIED:20260710T203457Z
LOCATION:7 Stages Theatre\, 1105 Euclid Ave NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://atlantafilmseries.tix.page/e/atlanta-experimental-fest
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Atlanta Micro Short Film Festival
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260711T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260712T000000
DTSTAMP:20260710T203459Z
UID:occ-1707@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Film Screening
DESCRIPTION:Over 120 micro shorts in one afternoon\, each six minutes or l
 ess\, from animation to horror to documentary.\n\nA single fast-moving aft
 ernoon packed with more than 120 short films\, every one of them clocking 
 in at six minutes or under. Filmmakers from around the world contribute ac
 ross the board: animation\, horror\, documentary\, comedy\, drama\, and ex
 perimental work. Presented by 7 Stages\, in a theatre that started life as
  a movie house.
GEO:33.7639125;-84.3509364
LAST-MODIFIED:20260710T203457Z
LOCATION:7 Stages Theatre\, 1105 Euclid Ave NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://atlantafilmseries.tix.page/e/atlanta-micro-short-film-festival
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Grease Sing-A-Long (1978)
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260801T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260801T170000
DTSTAMP:20260710T203459Z
UID:occ-1233@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Film Screening
DESCRIPTION:The 1978 movie musical with on-screen lyrics — sing every wo
 rd\, rated PG\, 105 minutes.\n\nThe 1978 film with John Travolta and Olivi
 a Newton-John as Danny and Sandy\, screened sing-along style with on-scree
 n lyrics for "Summer Nights\," "Greased Lightnin'\," and the rest. A summe
 r romance collides with 1950s high-school social order when the pair land 
 at the same school. Rated PG\, 1 hour 45 minutes\, and a live pre-show con
 cert on the house Mighty Allen Theatre Organ begins thirty minutes before 
 the film.
GEO:33.9536122;-84.5492054
LAST-MODIFIED:20260710T203458Z
LOCATION:The Strand Theatre\, 117 N Park Square
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://thestrand.my.salesforce-sites.com/ticket/#/instances/a0FPs0000
 0749iDMAQ
END:VEVENT
